ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/red-dead-redemption"><em>Red Dead Redemption</em></a>已于今天（8 月 17 日）面向<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/playstation-4">PlayStation 4</a>发布，其中包含<em>Undead Nightmare</em>扩展包和精选奖励内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/exclusive-bastilles-dan-smith-wants-to-soundtrack-red-dead-redemption-3-3300694">巴士底狱的丹·史密斯希望为《荒野大镖客：救赎 3》配乐</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-coming-to-playstation-5-backwards-compatibility-3479431">本月早些时候宣布</a>，这个版本的<em>Red Dead Redemption</em>是米德尔斯堡开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/double-eleven">Double Eleven</a>的作品。这两款游戏包括<em>年度游戏版</em>的额外内容，如经典战斧、爆炸步枪、金枪武器等。玩家还可以获得中心人物约翰·马斯顿（精明的商人和专家猎人）以及其他人的两套新服装。</p><p>简体中文和繁体中文、韩语、波兰语、巴西葡萄牙语、俄语和拉丁美洲西班牙语等新语言与所有其他受支持的语言一起出现。此外，还有 PlayStation 4 的奖杯和 Nintendo Switch 上的游戏内成就。</p><p>最后， <em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em>的硬核模式已在 PlayStation 4 端口上解锁，玩家面临的挑战包括生命值减半、死眼瞄准无法自动填充、商店物品成本增加和售价降低等。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480339" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480339" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3480339" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480339" class="wp-caption-text"> 《荒野大镖客：救赎》来源：Take-Two Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Red Dead Redemption</em>现在可以在 PlayStation 4 和 Nintendo Switch 上以 39.99 英镑（49.99 美元）的价格购买数字版，实体版将于 10 月 13 日发售。</p><p> Unlike the remasters of <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition"><em>Grand Theft Auto 3, Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas</em></a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition"><em>Grand Theft Auto: Vice City</em></a> released in 2021, the new versions of <em>Red Dead Redemption</em> appear to be running relatively reliably for players.</p><p> <a href="https://youtu.be/m9QmGxSKZ_4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Digital Foundry</em></a> &#39;s technical analysis of the experience of playing the game on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 4 Pro and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a> described it as a “serviceable but very conservative update”.</p><p> It was found that the game does suffer from a “very staccato and slightly choppy feel while playing at 30 [frames per second]” as a result of an animation pacing issue. While Digital Foundry conceded that this doesn&#39;t happen all of the time, the <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox">Xbox</a> versions don&#39;t share this particular problem.</p><p> Elsewhere, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two-interactive">Take-Two Interactive</a> CEO Strauss Zelnick suggested that it is <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-film-is-too-much-of-a-risk-suggests-publisher-3480504">too much of a financial risk to develop a <em>Red Dead Redemption</em> film or TV show</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-has-launched-on-ps4-and-nintendo-switch-3484532">&#39;Red Dead Redemption&#39; has launched on PS4 and Nintendo Switch</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
